00231 CHPMultiDataData::CHPMultiDataData(const std::string& filename, const std::list<std::wstring> *groupNames) 
00232 { 
00233         Clear();
00234         SetFilename(filename);
00235     if (groupNames == NULL)
00236     {
00237             DataGroupHeader dcHdr(MULTI_DATA_NAME);
00238             genericData.Header().AddDataGroupHdr(dcHdr);
00239         genericData.Header().SetNumDataGroups(1);
00240     }
00241     else
00242     {
00243         std::list<std::wstring>::const_iterator it;
00244         for (it = groupNames->begin(); it != groupNames->end(); it++)
00245         {
00246             DataGroupHeader dcHdr(*it);
00247             genericData.Header().AddDataGroupHdr(dcHdr);
00248         }
00249         genericData.Header().SetNumDataGroups((int)groupNames->size());
00250     }
00251         genericData.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->SetFileTypeId(CHP_MULTI_DATA_TYPE);
00252 }

00259 DataSetHeader *CHPMultiDataData::GetDataSetHeader(MultiDataType dataType)
00260 {
00261     int ng = genericData.Header().GetNumDataGroups();
00262     for (int ig=0; ig<ng; ig++)
00263     {
00264         DataGroupHeader &dh = genericData.Header().GetDataGroup(ig);
00265             int n = dh.GetDataSetCnt();
00266             for (int i=0; i<n; i++)
00267             {
00268                     DataSetHeader &h = dh.GetDataSet(i);
00269                     if (h.GetName() == MultiDataDataSetNames[(int)dataType])
00270                             return &h;
00271             }
00272     }
00273         return NULL;
00274 }

00276 void CHPMultiDataData::Clear()
00277 {
00278         for (map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo>::iterator it=dataSetInfo.begin(); it!=dataSetInfo.end(); ++it)
00279         {
00280                 DataSetInfo &info = it->second;
00281                 info.metricColumns.clear();
00282                 if (info.entries){ info.entries->Delete();  info.entries = 0; }
00283         }
00284         dataSetInfo.clear();
00285     dataTypeGroupNames.clear();
00286         genericData.Header().Clear();

00345 int CHPMultiDataData::GetDataGroupIndex(MultiDataType dataType)
00346 {
00347     const std::wstring &name = dataTypeGroupNames[dataType];
00348     int ng = genericData.Header().GetNumDataGroups();
00349     for (int ig=0; ig<ng; ig++)
00350     {
00351         DataGroupHeader &dh = genericData.Header().GetDataGroup(ig);
00352             if (dh.GetName() == name)
00353             return ig;

00355     return -1;

00370 void CHPMultiDataData::SetEntryCount(MultiDataType dataType, int32_t ln, int32_t maxln, const std::vector<ColumnInfo> &columns, const std::wstring &groupName)
00371 {
00372         DataSetInfo info;
00373         info.maxName = maxln;
00374         info.metricColumns = columns;
00375         info.entries = NULL;
00376         info.dataType = dataType;
00377         info.dataSetIndex = (int)dataSetInfo.size();
00378         dataSetInfo[dataType] = info;
00379 
00380         DataSetHeader dsHdr;
00381         dsHdr.SetRowCnt(ln);
00382         dsHdr.SetName(MultiDataDataSetNames[(int)dataType]);
00383         AddColumns(info, dsHdr);
00384 
00385     if (groupName.empty() == true)
00386         dataTypeGroupNames[dataType] = MULTI_DATA_NAME;
00387     else
00388         dataTypeGroupNames[dataType] = groupName;
00389         DataGroupHeader* dgHdr = GetDataGroupHeader(dataTypeGroupNames[dataType]);
00390         dgHdr->AddDataSetHdr(dsHdr);
00391 }

00740 void CHPMultiDataData::GetExtraMetricEntries(DataSetInfo *ds, int rowIndex, int colIndex, std::vector<affymetrix_calvin_parameter::ParameterNameValueType> &metrics)
00741 {
00742         int32_t ncols = (int32_t) ds->metricColumns.size();
00743         metrics.resize(ncols);
00744         for (int32_t icol=0; icol<ncols; icol++)
00745         {
00746                 metrics[icol].SetName(ds->metricColumns[icol].GetName());
00747                 switch (ds->metricColumns[icol].GetColumnType())
00748                 {
00749                 case ByteColType:
00750                         {
00751                                 int8_t val;
00752                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00753                                 metrics[icol].SetValueInt8(val);
00754                         }
00755                         break;
00756 
00757                 case UByteColType:
00758                         {
00759                                 u_int8_t val;
00760                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00761                                 metrics[icol].SetValueUInt8(val);
00762                         }
00763                         break;
00764 
00765                 case ShortColType:
00766                         {
00767                                 int16_t val;
00768                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00769                                 metrics[icol].SetValueInt16(val);
00770                         }
00771                         break;
00772 
00773                 case UShortColType:
00774                         {
00775                                 u_int16_t val;
00776                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00777                                 metrics[icol].SetValueUInt16(val);
00778                         }
00779                         break;
00780 
00781                 case IntColType:
00782                         {
00783                                 int32_t val;
00784                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00785                                 metrics[icol].SetValueInt32(val);
00786                         }
00787                         break;
00788 
00789                 case UIntColType:
00790                         {
00791                                 u_int32_t val;
00792                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00793                                 metrics[icol].SetValueUInt32(val);
00794                         }
00795                         break;
00796 
00797                 case FloatColType:
00798                         {
00799                                 float val;
00800                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00801                                 metrics[icol].SetValueFloat(val);
00802                         }
00803                         break;
00804 
00805                 case ASCIICharColType:
00806                         {
00807                                 string val;
00808                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00809                                 metrics[icol].SetValueAscii(val);
00810                         }
00811                         break;
00812 
00813                 case UnicodeCharColType:
00814                         {
00815                                 wstring val;
00816                                 ds->entries->GetData(rowIndex, colIndex++, val);
00817                                 metrics[icol].SetValueText(val);
00818                         }
00819                         break;
00820                 }
00821         }
00822 }

01077 
01078 DataSetInfo *CHPMultiDataData::OpenMultiDataDataSet(MultiDataType dataType)
01079 {
01080         map<MultiDataType, DataSetInfo>::iterator pos = dataSetInfo.find(dataType);
01081         if (pos != dataSetInfo.end())
01082         {
01083                 return &dataSetInfo[dataType];
01084         }
01085         //read metrics column data
01086         DataSetInfo info;
01087     if (dataTypeGroupNames.empty() == true)
01088     {
01089         std::map<std::wstring, MultiDataType> nameTypeMap;
01090         int nnames = sizeof(MultiDataDataSetNames) / sizeof(std::wstring);
01091         for (int iname=0; iname<nnames; iname++)
01092             nameTypeMap[MultiDataDataSetNames[iname]] = MultiDataDataTypes[iname];
01093         int ng = genericData.Header().GetDataGroupCnt();
01094         for (int ig=0; ig<ng; ig++)
01095         {
01096             DataGroupHeader &dh = genericData.Header().GetDataGroup(ig);
01097             std::wstring name = dh.GetName();
01098             int ns = dh.GetDataSetCnt();
01099             for (int is=0; is<ns; is++)
01100             {
01101                 DataSetHeader &h = dh.GetDataSet(is);
01102                 dataTypeGroupNames[nameTypeMap[h.GetName()]] = dh.GetName();
01103             }
01104         }
01105     }
01106         info.entries = genericData.DataSet(dataTypeGroupNames[dataType], MultiDataDataSetNames[dataType]);
01107         if (info.entries)
01108         {
01109                 info.entries->Open();
01110                 int32_t ncols = info.entries->Header().GetColumnCnt();
01111                 info.metricColumns.clear();
01112                 int startCol = 0;
01113                 if (dataType == ExpressionMultiDataType || dataType == ExpressionControlMultiDataType)
01114                 {
01115                         startCol = 2;
01116                 }
01117                 else if (dataType == GenotypeMultiDataType || dataType == GenotypeControlMultiDataType)
01118                 {
01119                         startCol = 3;
01120                 }
01121                 else if (dataType == CopyNumberMultiDataType)
01122                 {
01123                         startCol = 3;
01124                 }
01125                 else if (dataType == CytoMultiDataType)
01126                 {
01127                         startCol = 6;
01128                 }
01129                 else if (dataType == CopyNumberVariationMultiDataType)
01130                 {
01131                         startCol = 4;
01132                 }
01133                 else if (dataType == DmetCopyNumberMultiDataType)
01134                 {
01135                         startCol = 7;
01136                 }
01137                 else if (dataType == DmetMultiAllelicMultiDataType)
01138                 {
01139                         startCol = 17;
01140                 }
01141                 else if (dataType == DmetBiAllelicMultiDataType)
01142                 {
01143                         startCol = 8;
01144                 }
01145         else if (dataType == ChromosomeSummaryMultiDataType)
01146         {
01147             startCol = 9;
01148         }
01149         else if (dataType == SegmentCNMultiDataType ||
01150             dataType == SegmentLOHMultiDataType ||
01151             dataType == SegmentCNNeutralLOHMultiDataType ||
01152             dataType == SegmentNormalDiploidMultiDataType ||
01153             dataType == SegmentNoCallMultiDataType ||
01154             dataType == SegmentMosaicismMultiDataType)
01155                 {
01156                         startCol = 6;
01157                 }
01158                 else if (dataType == SegmentGenotypeConcordanceMultiDataType ||
01159             dataType == SegmentGenotypeDiscordanceMultiDataType ||
01160             dataType == SegmentCNLossLOHConcordanceMultiDataType ||
01161             dataType == SegmentCNNeutralLOHConcordanceMultiDataType ||
01162             dataType == SegmentHeteroUPDMultiDataType ||
01163             dataType == SegmentIsoUPDMultiDataType ||
01164             dataType == SegmentDenovoCopyNumberMultiDataType ||
01165             dataType == SegmentHemizygousParentOfOriginMultiDataType)
01166         {
01167             startCol = 11;
01168         }
01169         else if (dataType == FamilialSegmentOverlapsMultiDataType)
01170         {
01171             startCol = 5;
01172         }
01173                 else if (dataType == FamilialSamplesMultiDataType)
01174                 {
01175                         startCol = 7;
01176                 }
01177                 else if (dataType == AllelePeaksMultiDataType)
01178                 {
01179                         startCol = 3;
01180                 }
01181                 else if (dataType == MarkerABSignalsMultiDataType)
01182                 {
01183                         startCol = 4;
01184                 }
01185                 for (int32_t icol=startCol; icol<ncols; icol++)
01186                 {
01187                         info.metricColumns.push_back(info.entries->Header().GetColumnInfo(icol));
01188                 }
01189                 dataSetInfo[dataType] = info;
01190                 return &dataSetInfo[dataType];
01191         }
